{
    "Wait!": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_textAboveHeadEvent1",
    "Hello, Leo... My name's Linus.": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event2",
    "I've heard all about you, and your parrot family.": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event2_sv1",
    "It's really something special!": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event2_sv2",
    "Aye, lad... Linus lives on the mainland with the rest of us.": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Willy_event1",
    "After hearing your story... I wanted to help. So, I talked to Linus here and hatched a little plan.": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Willy_event1_sv1",
    "Go on, Linus... tell him.": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Willy_event2",
    "Leo...": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event3",
    "I'd like you to come back with us, to Stardew Valley.": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event3_sv1",
    "It's a beautiful place... not as warm as here, but still full of life... and I live right in the middle of it!": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event3_sv2",
    "I know the lay of the land, and many things about the waters, the trees, the animals, and more...": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event3_sv3",
    "You see... I'm a child of nature, too. You might say we're 'birds of a feather'.": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event3_sv4",
    "But, I'm getting old... And I'd like to teach someone all that I've learned before moving on...": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event3_sv5",
    "Leo... will you come back with us?": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event3_sv6",
    "will you come back with us?": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Linus_event3_sv7",
    "L... leave the island?": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Leo_event1",
    "I can take you back for a visit any time!": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Willy_event3",
    "But, lad.... You can't live here forever...": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Willy_event3_sv1",
    "You know, there are other children back home, too. I'm sure they'd love to meet ya...": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Willy_event3_sv2",
    "O... other kids?": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Leo_event2",
    "What do you think, @?": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Willy_event4",
    "Well, let's not forget... the choice is really up to Leo...": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Willy_event5",
    "I understand. This is Leo's home, after all.": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Willy_event6",
    "I...": "IslandSouth_6497428_leoMoved_Leo_event3",
